    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Support my work and get more weapons to play with:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275900/extras/0a88e0c2aca816a3a004a5ec70009c0b.avif?t=1770392701\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Machine Gun has a high rate of fire at the cost of accuracy. 20-round magazine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275900/extras/e15b19b65a89c36c3ece71a050b2692c.avif?t=1770392701\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Carbine combines accuracy with high Focus (zoom) allowing for some sniper action.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275900/extras/5c30763ff03d93792f62c8b15da29c41.avif?t=1770392701\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Coach Gun causes mayhem at close range.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275900/extras/aad7199125ed91b06c093db28a98f254.avif?t=1770392701\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Bow is difficult to master but very satisfying when you can.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275900/extras/27268562fc52fbef2b5c0212da8c6eac.avif?t=1770392701\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Repeater is a good all-around choice with good fire rate. 10+1 rounds capacity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275900/extras/0188633b0f131013cf67e3b686284130.avif?t=1770392701\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dual Pistols. High fire rate. 20+2 low-power rounds. Low recoil, medium spread that doesn't get much worse when moving.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275900/extras/8931176cb78897373cfea81be874aa05.avif?t=1770392701\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamite. 5 seconds fuse.</p>",
